SELECT a.attname
  FROM (
         SELECT indrelid, indkey, generate_subscripts(indkey, 1) idx
           FROM pg_index
          WHERE indrelid = '"poll_votes"'::regclass
            AND indisprimary
       ) i
  JOIN pg_attribute a
    ON a.attrelid = i.indrelid
   AND a.attnum = i.indkey[i.idx]
 ORDER BY i.idx
